# QuickTools

Free, privacy-first web tools (single-page).

## Tools
- Image Compressor (client-side, max 10MB)
- PDF Merge & Split (client-side via pdf-lib, max 15MB per file, total 20MB)
- QR Code Generator (client-side via qrcode)

## Deploy
1. Create a GitHub repository and push files.
2. Deploy to Netlify: connect repo or use Netlify Drop.
3. Add Google Analytics ID in index.html and AdSense code into ad sections.

